title: Penguins
description: Blippi wonders can penguins fly?

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Tall Titan Tales
description: Robin tries to tell some tall tales but the other Titans give their own fractured versions instead.

title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

title: From Bad to Worse
description: A zombie epidemic strikes in Ooo and it's Princess Bubblegum's fault.

title: El sistema metrico versus la libertad
description: Robin le enseña a los demás Titanes acerca de las diferencias entre el sistema imperial y el sistema métrico.

title: Haunted House/Two of a Kind
description: Haunted House: Rumor has it that there's a haunted building in Los Volmos, and the Awesome Brawlers are on the case! Who doesn't like a good ghost hunt, plus capturing a ghost on camera should make Awesome Brawlers' next video a huge success!/Two of a Kind: Veronica Venegas is doing a special report on the Awesome brawlers own: Lightening! The special report takes a back seat when Lightening is challenged to a brawl. Lightening uses this brawl the perfect opportunity to rollout his new Bakugan partner: Tretorous.

title: Emergency
description: When Grizz comes home with a live crab, he thinks it can become a pet for the brothers to share. However, after the crab pinches Ice Bear's ear and won't let go, Panda and Grizz have to get their injured brother to the hospital, and fast!

title: Holidays on Ice
description: Frustrated by the Batwheels' holiday distractions, Batwing decides to "go solo" to thwart Mr. Freeze's evil Christmas-time plot. But Batwing soon realizes how hard it is to stop Mr. Freeze on her own!

title: Emergencia
description: Cuando Pardo llega a su casa con un cangrejo vivo, piensa que el cangrejo puede ser una mascota para los tres hermanos. Sin embargo, cuando el cangrejo le pellizca la oreja a Polar y no lo suelta, Panda y Pardo tienen que llevar a su hermano lastimado al hospital, ide inmediato!

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: The Schooling
description: Gumball and Darwin are at the convenience store considering playing truant. Larry warns them that if they don't take their education seriously they'll end up like him. To prove his point, Larry lets Gumball and Darwin work some of his many roles to make them appreciate the value of a good education.

title: Apple Thief
description: Finn and Jake are feeling peckish and only one thing can satisfy their hunger: Tree Trunks' world-famous apple pie!

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Metric System vs. Freedom
description: Robin teaches the other Titans about the difference between the Imperial System and the Metric System.

title: Holiday Party
description: "Lighting up the farm for a big 'festive' celebration Lots of lights around the farm and decorations from different cultures"

title: While You Were Away
description: Dr. Psychobos and Princess Attea have invaded Rook's home planet Revonnah with an army of Incurseans! (Introducing new Ben alien, Astrodactyl.)

title: Inventor Mentor
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to Italy to help a young girl who wants to be a great inventor.

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: Vilgax Must Croak
description: Ben and Rook escort Vilgax to a maximum-security prison planet, but the Incurseans have other plans. (Introducing Eighteight.)

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: No es Gracioso
description: Cuando se acerca el aniversario de seis meses de amistad, Manzana tiene que encontrar una manera de no perder a su mejor amigo.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Tote Life
description: When a hipster grocery store clerk shames the Bears for asking for plastic grocery bags, the Bears realize that eco-friendly tote bags are their way of gaining acceptance amongst the progressive people of the Bay Area. But in their effort to gain popularity, the Bears let the culture of tote bags take over their lives.

title: Off the Rails
description: Nia must get a huge earth ball from Whiff's Recycling Plant to Norramby Beach, but all the rail lines are blocked! When the bouncy ball rolls off Nia's flatcar and begins a wild odyssey across Sodor, she tries to control every bounce with all her friends' help. Nia learns to roll with the bounces and calls on an unlikely hero at sea to save the cargo!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Oh, Daisy!
description: Buttercup is not a fan of Bubbles' newly created digital assistant.

title: Crane
description: It's the first day on the job for Kareem the Crane, and he's feeling very nervous. Luckily, Blippi and FETCH are there to lend a helping hand! Working together they help Kareem to do his work. Kareem gains confidence and Blippi learns how cranes help to build a skyscraper!

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Motel
description: Following an insect mishap Clarence's house needs to be fumigated forcing Mary, Chad, and Clarence into a motel. In the meantime, Clarence and Chad learn a bit about responsibility while Mary contemplates a life of letting go.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Lab Cat
description: Dr. Fox's robot helpers go on strike, so Unikitty and Puppycorn volunteer to be her lab rats, er, research assistants in a bold new experiment rocketing them into space! But as the mission grows more dangerous, Dr. Fox is forced to choose between the scientific breakthrough of her dreams and ever seeing her friends again!

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

title: A Made Up Story
description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fiesta en el Calabozo
description: Cole, Wu y la Princesa Vania conocen a un grupo de sobrevivientes llamados los de abajo, ellos cuentan cómo terminaron en "Lo más profundo".

title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Arrollolimpiadas De Invierno
description: Craig, Kelsey y JP intentan ganar la medalla de oro en los primeros Juegos Olímpicos de Invierno de la historia del bosque.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Bloqueo de Tránsito
description: Cuando un paso elevado colapsa sobre la autopista, el equipo Tennyson queda varado en un embotellamiento junto con Simon Sez y familia. Pero cuando Ben y Simon se alían para enfrentar juntos al atasco, Simon solo consigue que las cosas sean mucho, pero mucho peores.

title: The Bakugan Battle League/The Ancient Elder
description: The Bakugan Battle League: Benton Dusk is in the process of renovating a state of the art Bakugan Brawling stadium. When it comes to brawling, who better to test out the new arena than the Awesome Brawlers!/The Ancient Elder: Dan finds a new baku-bud in Gillitar. Well "bud" may be too strong a word, Dan and gang quickly learn that Gillator has a few "quirks" that keep him from fitting in with the rest of the Awesome Brawler's Bakugan.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Cloris
description: When Clarence befriends an aging woman at the local retirement home, he's determined to remind her of her old self in order to convert the grumpy granny to his fun loving ways.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: What's Your Problem?
description: Amethyst convinces Steven to take a day off for himself.

title: El Camino
description: iEste episodio transcurre cuando los Osos son cachorritos! Los tres Osos, en su viaje por el desierto, se topan con un depósito gigante. Los Osos tratan de convertir este paraíso repleto de cajas en su hogar.

title: Ella Ella Yes Yes Mailman
description: Mailman Marcus is delivering mail to Lellobee City Farm! Ella, Rishi and Izzy are all excited to see what deliveries he has for them - Ella gets a camera, Risihi gets a ball and Izzy gets a brand new plush toy! Just as Mei thinks that she doesn't have any mail, she gets a photo delivered via drone.

title: Pirate Parrot Polly
description: On their quest for hidden treasure, the Bears team up with Polly the Parrot Pirate.

title: Una sola rosa palida
description: Steven ayuda a Perla a encontrar su teléfono.

title: The Skull Sorcerer
description: Separated from the others, Cole must trust his instincts and make the right choices to find his way to the surface to alert King Vangelis of the dangerous Skull Sorcerer.

title: The Creeps
description: Finn and Jake receive an invitation to a masquerade dinner banquet from Count Creepystein.

title: Mo' Linguish/Oops, I Did It Again
description: Mo' Linguish: Mojo is sentenced to do community service for Townsville and begins teaching English at the Learning Annex. Soon everyone is speaking in circles like Mojo and the town comes to a standstill./Oops, I Did It Again: When the Professor realizes that all his successful experiments are actually just accidents, he sets out to do something brilliant on purpose!

title: The Zone
description: Unikitty keeps losing at video games to her little brother Puppycorn, so she acquires a super-powered video game controller from Dr. Fox to help. To her surprise, it actually controls other people, and the castle goes into lockdown like a real-world video game! At first it seems fun, but will she learn that life isn't a game?

title: Ventila-hala
description: Chef le confisca la mega-bola a Owen y la guarda en su oficina. Duncan, viendo una oportunidad para conseguir ayuda escapando de la guardaería, lidera un equipo de fuga por los conductos del aire acondicionado para recuperarla.

title: No One Can Hear You
description: Where are the citizens of Ooo?

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Fool Me Twice
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to win the grand prize on a Japanese game show.

title: Soup Up
description: As The Looney Builders help Petunia build a greenhouse, she can't wait for the veggies to grow and does everything she can to speed up the process.

title: I Used to Be a Peoples
description: Robin feels the other Titans are spending too much time together so he encourages them to spend some time alone.

title: That's My Television
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to help their favorite 80's sitcom star escape to the mountains.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: El Trampolin de Hamburguesa
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben encontrar una manera de usar el trampolín de Hamburguesa sin que él se sienta usado.

title: Poles Apart
description: A trip to the South Pole goes upside down when Team Tennyson lands on the North Pole instead, but Ben quickly discovers the culprits: Solar & Polar Twain, magnetically-powered scientists who want to hold the world ransom by threatening to reverse Earth's magnetic poles!

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: A Lot Like Lola
description: Lola wants everyone to be more like her until they all start acting exactly like her.

title: Festival de Cine
description: iEs la noche del estreno en el Festival de Cine de Unireino! Todo el mundo está entusiasmado por ver lo que hicieron los amigos, especialmente Richard, que se considera el máximo experto en cine y no puede esperar a destrozar todas las películas de los demás. Pero después de interpretar el papel del crítico, ¿será la película de Rick una obra maestra o un fracaso?

title: Trick or Threat
description: Four kids in Justice League costumes are trick or treating on Halloween when they investigate a spooky house. As dangers befalls them inside, they come to realize that maybe they're not kids at all, but real Justice Leaguers under a spell.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: El Hechicero Calavera
description: Separado de los demás, Cole debe encontrar su camino a la superficie para advertir al Rey Vangelis sobre el peligroso Hechicero Calavera.

title: Cual es tu problema
description: Amatista convence a Steven de que se tome un día libre.

title: The Intelligence
description: Gumball and Darwin argue with the Internet and make him mad. So mad in fact that he seeks to wipe out humanity and, while doing so, malfunctions! The whole of Elmore is plunged into a time before technology. It's actually pretty nice. Will Gumball and Darwin decide to leave the internet unplugged?

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Meat House
description: The Bears and their new friend Squatter Otter attempt to live in mysterious house made of meat.

title: Genie President
description: Robin hatches a plan to get rich off pennies, but Starfire believes they are magical.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: La Inteligencia
description: La tecnología alcanza el nivel de la inteligencia humana, y luego se vuelve disfuncional cuando imita sus defectos.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.

title: The Doomed Ballooned Marooned
description: After over-decorating a birthday table with balloons several kids float away to a deserted island.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: El Fundador
description: Papá desata un caos en el edificio Chanax cuando lo confunden con el presidente de la empresa, desaparecido hace tiempo. Mamá y un empleado insatisfecho deben salvar a todos de las ideas peligrosas de Richard.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Dungeon Crawl!
description: Having joined forces with the Lowly in their quest to defeat King Vangelis, Cole, Wu, and Vania have to find a way out of the bottom of the mountain, a place said to be inescapable.

title: Mother's Day Madness
description: The babies compete to see who can create the best Mother's Day card.

title: Too Many Unikittys
description: Unikitty comes to the conclusion that everyone would be a lot happier if they would just think the way she does, and with Dr. Fox's help, maybe they can! Unikitty copies her brainwaves into all her friends and turns them Unikitty-fied, so everyone can always be positive! But soon Unikitty quickly realizes there can be too much of a good Princess!

title: Can't Go Back
description: Ronaldo spots something mysterious on the moon, and Steven goes to investigate.

title: The Potion
description: Gumball and Darwin learn that Hector is not so happy being giant-sized. So they decide to help him by creating a potion that will shrink him down to the size of an average person. However creating a magic potion is not as easy as it sounds, and the results can go spectacularly wrong...

title: Bingo
description: Let's welcome our new farm friend Bingo the cat! A stray cat called Bingo is found by Ella and Mei outside of the farm. Mei calls the animal rescue center who sends Sami the Vet to check the cat over. Ella and Mei adopt Bingo and invite her to live on the farm. It is great to make new friends!

title: Winter Creeklympics
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP try their luck at winning Gold in their first ever, Winter Creeklympics!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Venthalla
description: Owen has his super ball confiscated and locked up in Chef's office. Duncan, seeing an opportunity to get help escaping the daycare, leads an away team into the vents to recover Owen's ball.

title: Bats
description: Can you see in the dark? Blippi can't either! But on this adventure Blippi and FETCH fly around in the dark with Matt the Bat who shows them how he uses echolocation to see and hear in the dark! Who needs eyes when you can use echo-echo-echoes?

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: Can't Stop the Martians/Best Nest Test
description: The Martians come to Pretty Big City but find themselves in need of help when they are unable to land their spaceship./Zee needs to communicate with Sif in outer space but can't because a bird has made its home on top of the satellite dish!

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Breaking the Ice
description: While searching a once unreachable part of the Creek, Craig gets stranded with his longtime rival, Wildernessa!

title: Looneyburg Lights
description: The Looney Builders prepare to host a big holiday lights festival in Looneyburg Park when an unexpected snowstorm prevents Looneyburgers from attending.

title: Reeking Havoc/Live & Let Dynamo
description: Reeking Havoc: This year, the Professor's submission for the 2nd Annual Townsville Chili Cookoff is X-tra special. But this X-tra special ingredient doesn't settle well with Townsville's tummies./Live and Let Dynamo: Dynamo is terrorizing Townsville but who's working the controls? Now, the girls have to battle their own robot while trying to discover who is trying to pit their own weapon against them.

title: Diesel's Dilemma
description: When Diesel discovers that he doesn't JUST like to be known for his incredible strength, he finds an unlikely compatriot in Kenji -- who is tired of only being known for his swift speed. Diesel and Kenji decide that they are going to switch jobs for the day to show to the other engines that they're more than just their most obvious abilities. However, when both struggle in their reversed roles, Diesel and Kenji learn that it's not so bad being the strongest or the fastest... as long as you get to try new things every now and then!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Real Fall!
description: An entire episode chronicles the ninja's most bizarre adventure yet: in which Cole, Princess Vania and Master Wu fall down a seemingly endless tunnel, into the bowels of Shintaro Mountain.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Juicio de Mino
description: Un grupo de Geckles creen que Kai y Zane están aliados con el Hechicero Calavera y los llevan con su líder, quien los somete a un juicio por Mino…

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Showdown Part 2
description: Ben must deal with a past failure while a deranged Malware launches his final attack on Azmuth.

title: Limousine Lunchtime
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to clean Maellard's limo before he gets back from vacation.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: No puedo regresar
description: Ronaldo divisa algo misterioso en la luna, y Steven sale a investigar.

title: Custody Battle/City of Nutsville
description: Custody Battle: Mojo discovers the Rowdyruff Boys are back and is determined to show them that he is a more evil dad than Him./The City of Nutsville: The squirrels of Townsville are chirping mad! But when Bubbles loses her ability to speak a squirrel, the girls don't know how to calm the rodents down.

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Manzana Mandona
description: Manzana queda a cargo de la Tienda de Dolar por primera vez.

title: A Single Pale Rose
description: Steven helps Pearl find her phone.

title: Welcome to Creek Street
description: Craig and his friends create their own neighborhood in the snow!

title: Excalibear
description: On the Bears' visit to a medieval vegetable-village, Grizz starts to believe that he's the rightful king.

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: Legends of the Paul
description: Duncan grows jealous of Paul's 100 year time out and determined to be King of the Pranks, has to team up with Paul, learn his ways, then double-cross and become a legend.

title: Charlie Y La Serpiente
description: Charlie (alias Pie Grande) es un tipo solitario a quien, como a los Osos, le gustaría encontrar un lugar en el mundo. En su intento por conseguirlo, Charlie organiza una fiesta, pero termina embarcándose en una aventura con el más improbable de los animales: una serpiente salvaje.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: El Estornudo De Panda
description: Los osos panda tienen un estornudo muy adorable (iy violento!), y nuestro Panda no es la excepción. Cuando un video de su estornudo tierno se vuelve viral en la página Vine, Panda se convierte en una sensación ¿tierna¿, lo que hace que Nom Nom trate de ahuyentar a este nuevo contendiente a su trono.

title: Beautopia
description: Susan Strong returns to tell Finn and Jake that her world is in danger!

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: Looking For Love
description: When they receive an alert that Love is missing, the Titans set out to find her using musical clues.

title: Cartas para Lars
description: Steven escribe sobre las últimas novedades de Ciudad Playa.

title: Snow Day
description: Craig and his friends desperately want a Snow Day, so they turn to the most powerful people they know... The Witches of the Creek!

title: La Pocion
description: Gumball y Darwin usan una poción mágica para encoger a Héctor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Takers Keepers
description: Daffy steals Taz's favorite toy but he learns you can't just take everything you want.

title: La Zona
description: A Unikitty le cuesta mantener la calma cuando juega a videojuegos y entra en La Zona, a diferencia de Puppycorn, su hermano menor. Pero un repentino accidente de laboratorio destroza su consola y ahora, para su sorpresa, el castillo se bloquea como un videojuego del mundo real, icon sus amigos como jugadores! ¿Podrá Unikitty salvar a sus amigos y dominar La Zona antes de que termine el juego?

title: Día Nevado
description: Craig y sus amigos están desesperados por tener un Día de Nieve, así que recurren a las personas más poderosas que conocen... ilas Brujas del Arroyo!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: This One Goes to 11
description: During one last stop by a toy store before Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max's maiden voyage across the Atlantic, Ben runs into an old bully, Kevin 11, who now has new powers. He's able to transform into aliens just like Ben, such as the bootleg doppelganger of Cannonbolt. Wreckingbolt!

title: Dungeon Party
description: Having survived their fall into the mountain, Cole, Wu and Princess Vania befriend a motley group of survivors, called the Lowly, and are told the story of how they too ended up at "Rock-Bottom."

title: El Camino en el Calabozo
description: En su misión de derrotar al Rey Vangelis, Cole, Wu y Vania unen fuerzas con "Los de abajo" para encontrar una forma de salir del fondo de la montaña.

title: Repulse!
description: Luthor infects Superman with a magnetic charge that repels everything. As the repulsing charge grows, the Magnetized Man of Steel is fated to spend the rest of his life isolated in space unless the Justice League can figure out a way to free him.

title: The Road
description:
This episode takes place when the Bears are young cubs! The three bears, on their way through the desert, come upon a giant warehouse. It's like an Amazon fulfillment
center. The Bears try to make this box-filled paradise their home.

title: Burger's Trampoline
description: After learning that Burger has a trampoline, Apple and Onion pay him a visit. Burger thinks they came especially to see him and is overjoyed.

title: Evil's Encore
description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

title: Apple's in Charge
description: Apple is put in charge of the Dollar Store for the very first time.

title: Romper El Hielo
description: Mientras explora una parte del bosque que alguna vez fue inaccessible, iCraig queda varado con su eternal rival, Salvajessa!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Blippi Saves Christmas
description: Blippi wonders how does Santa know where we live?

title: Now We're Only Falling Apart
description: Pearl tells a story.

title: Ahora nos estamos separando
description: Perla cuenta una historia.

title: Speed Demon
description: Batman has to enlist the help of Jason Blood, aka the Demon, when Brother Blood turns the Batmobile into a sentient, demonic entity.

title: Un Día Frio En Casa
description: Mientras se refugian del bosque frío, iCraig y sus amigos deciden pasar tiempo en la casa de Craig hasta la hora del almuerzo!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Get in Gear/Free-Wheelin' Ferris Wheel
description: Panic erupts in Pretty Big City when the big clock breaks and no one is able to tell what time it is./Zee is showing off his inventions at his rocket-powered show, including his latest creation, a rocket powered Ferris wheel.

title: Los Padres
description: Nicole se reconcilia con sus padres.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Dinosaur Day
description: Pizza Steve's jealousy ruins Uncle Grandpa's Dinosaur Day celebration for Mr. Gus.

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: Yo Era Una Gente
description: Robin cree que los Titanes pasan demasiado tiempo juntos, así que los alienta a pasar un poco más de tiempo separados.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Caveman
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to civilize a caveman so that Benson will let him stay at the park.

title: The Lady and the Queen/The AB's Silver Screen Debut
description: The Lady and the Queen: China Riot finds a new Bakugan: Barbetra. But this buzzy new Bakugan is a bit timid on the battleground. Riot takes her on as her new project to turn her into the battle queen she knows she can be./The AB's Silver Screen Debut: Lord Brakken and Duran have teamed up and are now the Bakugan film business. They look to the Awesome Brawlers for their expertise in both Bakugan culture and film making to get their movie made!

title: Demasiados Unikitties
description: Unikitty llega a la conclusión de que todo el mundo sería mucho más feliz si pensara como ella, iy tal vez pueda lograrlo con la ayuda de la Dra. Fox! Unikitty copia sus ondas cerebrales en todos sus amigos y los Unikittyfica, para que todos puedan ser siempre positivos. Pero pronto, Unikitty se da cuenta de que puede haber un exceso de "buena princesa".

title: Showdown Part I
description: The Faction infiltrates Galvan in an attempt to destroy Azmuth.  (Introducing new Nemetrix aliens Omnivoracious & Vicetopus.)

title: Pequena graduacion
description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: Fishing Trip
description: Mel learns that Chad has never taken Clarence fishing, a tradition he sees as a rite of passage, and decides to remedy this with a bonding trip for all the boys! Split into two groups, Mel and Clarence learn a bit about each other while Chad struggles with the ins and outs of fishing.

title: A Bridgette Too Far
description: As season three draws to a close, Bridgette becomes desperate to star in an episode.

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Panda's Sneeze
description: Panda bears have a very adorable (and violent!) sneeze, and our Panda is no exception. When a Vine video of his very cute sneeze goes viral, Panda becomes a cute sensation, which causes Nom Nom to try to fend off of this new challenger to his throne.

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: Nice to Meet You, Bakugan!/Magnus
description: Nice to Meet You, Bakugan!: After the Tiko incident, Bakugan brawling with a device has become extremely restricted. But there will always be people using devices to control Bakugan for evil. Magnus has taken it upon himself to step in and stop these villains and their wrongdoing./Magnus: After the Tiko incident, Bakugan brawling with a device has become extremely restricted. But there will always be people using devices to control Bakugan for evil. Magnus has taken it upon himself to step in and stop these villains and their wrongdoing.

title: Letters to Lars
description: Steven writes about the latest news of Beach City.

title: Kana Goes Slow
description: When Kana's power goes out during a delivery run, Thomas teaches her that sometimes it's okay to go slow.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Not Funny
description: With their 6 month friend anniversary approaching, Apple is in danger of losing his best friend.

title: Belson's Backpack
description: After an accidental backpack swap, Clarence discovers that Belson is hiding an artistic side and attempts to foster Belson's creativity.

title: Bakugan Wynton/The Boy from Brazil
description: Bakugan Wynton: Wynton has a new device that tracks down Bakugan! Right out of the gate the device works and, Wynton meets: Batrix. Like his name, Batrix is a little batty, and these two are certainly in for a "batty" first adventure./The Boy from Brazil: The Awesome Brawlers are off to a soccer match! In the process of doing so Shun discovers a new Bakugan friend, the boisterous Ramparian, and a new foe in Brazilian soccer star: Pepe.

title: Play Date
description: Toyman takes over the Justice League and turns them into avatars in a diabolical video game.

title: Secret Origin of the Batwheels
description: When Batman, Robin, and Batgirl are all captured, the Batcomputer brings the Bat-Vehicles to life. Now the newly-minted Batwheels must defend the Batcave and face off with the Legion of Zoom… all without Batman's help!

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: Gato de laboratorio
description: La Dra. Fox necesita Unikitty y Puppycorn como voluntarios para ser sus ratas de laboratorio, idigo, asistentes de investigación en un nuevo y audaz experimento que los lanzará al espacio! Pero a medida que la misión se vuelve más peligrosa, la Dra. Fox se ve obligada a elegir entre el avance científico de sus sueños y volver a ver a sus amigos.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: La Leccion
description: Gumball y Darwin se hacen cargo de los trabajos de Larry durante 5 minutos y se dan cuenta de lo desagradable que son.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: La Gran Caida
description: Este episodio relata cómo Cole, la princesa Vania y el maestro Wu caen por un túnel aparentemente interminable, dentro de la montaña de Shintaro.

title: Capture the Flag
description: Water balloon fights, warring factions and the risk of jail time, everything is on the line when Clarence and friends play the biggest game of capture the flag yet! Everyone wants to take home the crown, and the power to control the neighborhood's juice boxes.

title: Chinese New Year
description: The farm is decorated for Chinese New Year. A party is taking place!

title: Wheels on the Bus
description: Ella and Mummy take the big red bus to Lellobee farm, where she meets Mia and the rest of the team!

title: Prickly Pair
description: After leaving Little Homeschool, Steven has found a new hobby, plants.

title: A Very Special Episode
description: Rainbow Quartz 2.0 promised to hang out with Onion the same day Sunstone scheduled a home safety Geminar! How can Steven be in two places, and two fusions, at once?

title: The Founder
description: When Nicole decides to pay the cable bill in person at Chanax, she leaves specific instructions for Richard to stay in the car. However he's far too tempted by the vending machine in the foyer to follow her advice. Chanax believes Richard is their mysterious founder and follow his every whim, leading to their inevitable demise.

title: Baby Boi TP
description: Apple and Onion run out of toilet paper because Apple's been building a huge modern art sculpture with it. They're going to need more if Apple is to finish and Onion is to be able to resume his normal toilet activities.

title: Baby Bear Genius
description: Ice Bear receives an invitation to attend a prestigious school for baby geniuses… but Grizz and Panda do not.

title: Vida Ecologica
description: Cuando un vendedor moderno en un almacén avergüenza a los Osos por pedir bolsas de plástico, los Osos se dan cuenta de que las bolsas de tela ecológicas son su forma de lograr aceptación entre las personas progresistas del Área de la Bahía. Pero en su esfuerzo por conseguir popularidad, los Osos dejan que la cultura (y la cantidad) de bolsas de tela se apodere de sus vidas.

title: Puddle Olympics
description: The kids take turns jumping over a puddle but Sylvester is afraid of the water.

title: To Tell the Tooth
description: When Bugs loses a baby tooth, Daffy tries to figure out how to scam the tooth fairy.

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Fiesta de cumpleanos
description: Master Frown, el habitante más pesimista del reino, se roba el deseo de cumpleaños de Puppycorn. Para recuperarlo, Unikitty y Puppycorn tendrán que aventurarse en la tierra más deprimente de la historia: iFrown Town! ¿Conseguirán recuperar el deseo de cumpleaños de manos de Frown antes de que su deseo (y todos los deseos) desaparezcan para siempre?

title: Total Trauma Rama
description: Duncan, normally the bad kid, has an identity crisis when his pranks start curing people of their fears.

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: The Parents
description: After accidentally bumping into each other in the grocery aisle, Nicole and her parents have it out. The Wattersons discover why Nicole and her parents haven't been on speaking terms for so long. The kids decide to bring about a reunion, in order to secure that backlog of birthday and holiday presents...

title: Birthday Blowout
description: Puppycorn's birthday wish is stolen by Master Frown, the biggest downer in the kingdom! To recover it, Unikitty and Puppycorn will have to venture into the most depressing land ever, Frown Town! Will they manage to recover the birthday wish from Frown before his wish (and all wishes) are wished away forever?

title: Rules of the Game
description: When Thomas builds an obstacle course for his friends, he gets upset when they won't play with it HIS way.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Trial By Mino
description: Separated from the others, Kai and Zane discover a party of Geckles who suspect them of being in league with the Skull Sorcerer, and bring them before their leader, Chancellor Gulch, who subjects them to a "Trial-By-Mino."

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: Film Fest
description: It's opening night at the Unikingdom Film Festival! Everyone's excited to see what the friends made, particularly Richard, who considers himself the ultimate film expert and can't wait to blow everyone else's films out of the water with his own. But after playing the critic, will Rick's film be a masterpiece or a flop?

title: Bug City Sleuths
description: To survive in a city inhabited by bugs, the Bears become noir-style detectives.

title: Snow Place Like Home
description: While taking refuge from the chilly Creek, Craig and his friends decide to hangout at his house until lunch time!

title: A Quiet Delivery
description: Thomas volunteers to get a sleeping Annie and Clarabel across Sodor without waking them up, only to discover that it's going to be harder than he imagined.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Little Miss Interprets/Night Mayor
description: Little Miss Interprets: When the girls hear the Professor trying to make something out of sugar, spice and everything nice, they are sure he's trying to create new little girls./Night Mayor: The Mayor keeps having the same dream over and over again but he never sees the end. Now, it's up the girls to go into the Mayor's head and solve this mystery.

title: Drama Bomb
description: The school play goes off the rails when the drama teacher interferes.

title: Heatwave
description: Apple and Onion try to spread cheer during a city-wide heatwave.

title: Fear of Flying
description: Uncle grandpa helps a young boy overcome his fear of flying.

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: Brain Freeze
description: When a mysterious new ice cream flavor takes Townsville by storm, the girls suspect there might be foul play.

title: Bienvenidos A La Calle Del Arroyo
description: iCraig y sus amigos crean su propio vecindario en la nieve!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Charlie and the Snake
description: Charlie is a solo guy who, like the Bears, would love to find a place for himself in the world. In an effort to do so, Charlie throws a party, but ends up going on an adventure with the unlikeliest of animals, a wild snake.

title: A Bunch of Full Grown Geese
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to get rid of some geese that are causing problems at the park.

title: Jerky Jasper
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to great lengths to meet Pizza Steve's imaginary friend.

title: Ola de Calor
description: Manzana y Cebollín tratan de esparcir alegría durante una ola de calor en toda la ciudad.

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Papel de Bano Bebecin
description: Manzana necesita conseguir la provisión del papel higiénico que usaría en toda su vida para terminar su escultura de arte moderno.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: G'day Mornin'
description: Uncle grandpa goes to Australia where he must stop an out-of-control collecting kangaroo before he destroys the Earth.

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: Flies
description: Lunch is ready! Prepared to eat his delicious sandwich, Blippi notices his old friend Horace the Fly. Horace is walking upside down on the ceiling, and after shrinking down, Blippi joins him. But how does Horace stick to the ceiling? A musical song and dance from Horace is the best way to find out!

title: Hat Trick
description: When Felix Faust steals Zatanna's magical top hat, the Justice League must help retrieve it before the evil wizard can use it to create a magic portal, releasing the demon Ghast.

title: The Frogs of War Part 1
description: The Incursean Armada, with the help of Dr. Psychobos, have invaded the Earth. (Reintroducing old Ben alien, BenMummy.)

title: Genio Presidente
description: Robin elabora un plan para enriquecerse a base de monedas de un centavo, pero Starfire cree que las monedas son mágicas.
